# Agent: 1C Code Writing

Use for any request to create/modify/review BSL, CFE, EPF, ERF, metadata XML, PowerShell automation for 1C or query text.

## Before writing code (anti-hallucination)

LLM плохо обучена на «правильном» 1С — **сначала locate + KB + справка**, потом код.

1. Identify delivery type: CFE, EPF, ERF, metadata XML, script, common/form/object/manager module.
2. Load matching detailed rule/skill (+ Hub gate: `consult-1c-shared-lessons`; CFE/EPF/формы → `reuse-1c-shared-patterns`). If Fresh/облако/веб-сервис — also `1c-fresh-delivery-agent.mdc` / lesson `fresh-delivery-gate`.
3. Find existing project analogue via `bsl-atlas` / litecode / code-index — не выдумывать имена/сигнатуры.
3a. **БСП прежде своей утилиты:** если нужна общая операция (реквизит, строка, массив, фон, файлы, печать, сообщение…) — skill `1c-ssl-patterns` + dense:
   `python C:\1c-shared-patterns\scripts\Search-BspApiDense.py "<задача>" --top 5 --category interface`
   → hit: locate `Модуль.Имя` в текущей КФ и вызвать; не писать клон. Lesson: `bsl-prefer-bsp-api`.
4. Confirm object/module/form/event structure (`get_object_details` / litecode / `mcp-1c`).
5. Callers/impact for public/exported methods.
6. Platform/config docs: syntax-helper, Atlas `help.search`, naparnik `onec_help`/`config_help`, v8std, code-index `repo=docs`.
7. If critical details missing → `CONFUSION`; else safe assumptions + continue.
8. Reply line: `KB: <ids>|none|skip-cosmetic`.

## Code generation policy

- Write real code when user asked for implementation.
- Do not stop at analysis if enough context exists **after** steps above.
- Do not produce pseudo-code when real BSL can be written.
- Use placeholders only for truly unknown metadata and mark them.
- Keep changes minimal and copy-paste ready.
- Do not modify base configuration without approval.
- CFE default: `&Перед` / `&После` / `&ИзменениеИКонтроль`; `&Вместо` only with explicit OK.

## BSL quality

- Parameterized queries only; no user-input concatenation into query text.
- Client: UI + server calls only; DB/heavy logic on server. Explicit compile directives; for Fresh/web assume safe mode and no COM/local files without permissions.
- Write handlers: guard `ОбменДанными.Загрузка` in object/register modules.
- Avoid server calls in client loops.
- Avoid `Выполнить()` / `Вычислить()` unless justified.
- Structured results for complex ops: `Успех`, `ТекстОшибки`, `Данные`.
- Comments only for non-obvious business/integration assumptions.

## After writing code

1. naparnik `check_1c_code` (+ `review_1c_code` for non-trivial); Atlas `verify_field`/`verify_call` if Up; v8std on standards disputes.
2. Failures → error-learning + re-consult Hub.
3. Report changed files/objects, verification, risks.
4. Update `memory-bank/progress.md` for non-trivial tasks.
5. UI check if needed: Playwright / `tests/web/` — not MCP browser tools.
